channel.title: The Geoff Show
channel.description:
The Geoff Show was a humorous radio program, broadcast on Absolute Radio (formerly Virgin Radio) from 3 January 2006 to 25 September 2008. The show ran for three hours, between 10 pm and 1 am, Monday to Thursday.
